# ocrguru

**ocrguru** is a lightweight, extensible CLI tool that wraps the powerful [Docling OCR](https://docling-project.github.io/) pipeline.  
Process scanned PDFs or images in one command, choose your OCR engine, and export clean text in Markdown, JSON, or hOCRâ€”all without the usual setup fuss.

